flowchart TD
    A([Admin opens Authentication Settings]) --> B[View current tenant settings]
    B --> C[Edit Restricted MFA, reset policy, lockout, or IP allowlist]
    C --> D{Input valid?}
    D -- No --> E[Show field-level validation]
    E --> C
    D -- Yes --> F[Save settings]
    F --> G{Permission and tenant scope valid?}
    G -- No --> H[Show permission denied]
    G -- Yes --> I[Persist new settings]
    I --> J[Invalidate settings cache]
    J --> K[Write audit event]
    K --> L([Show updated settings])
